<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[المجرّد]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَعَلَ بفتح العين، يفعُل بضمها<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[د]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[حَصَدَ]</span>: حَصْد الزرع: معروف.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">ويقال:</span> حصدهم بالسيف.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[ر]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[حَصَر]</span>: الحَصْر: الحبس.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">ويقال:</span> حصره: أي ضيَّق عليه.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">والحُصْر:</span> اعتقال البطن، وصاحبه محصور،<span class="c5"> وقال بعضهم:</span> لا يقال إِلا في البول.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">ويقال:</span> حَصَر الرجلُ بعيره: إِذا شدَّ عليه الحصار، وبعير محصور.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[حَصَل]</span>: يقال: حصل عليه من حَقي كذا: أي بقي.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>و <span class="c4">[حصا]</span>: الحصو: المنع، قال <span class="c2">«١»</span>:<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>ألا تخاف اللهَ إِذ حَصَوْتني ... حقي بلا ذنبٍ وإِذ عَيَّنْتَني<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>... فَعَل بفتح العين يَفعِل بكسرها<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c4">[ب]</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c4">[حَصَب]</span>: حصَبت الرجلَ بالحصباء:<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>إِذا رَمَيْتَه.<span class="c5"> وفي الحديث:</span> قال بعضهم:<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أَحْصِبُه لكم؟ يعني الحجاج بن يوسف.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c4">[م]</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span class="c4">[حَصمَ]</span>: أي ضرط.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c4">[ي]</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span><span class="c4">[حَصَا]</span>: حصاه: رماه بالحصى.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c5">وحصيَ الرجلُ:</span> أصابته الحصاة في مثانته.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
